                        Fairwinds
                        Golf Course

[fairwinds_golfer.jpg]


                            The Jim Fazio-designed Fairwinds Golf Club opened in 1991 and
   continues to earn accolades and praise.  Recently voted as one of the
   top three golf courses on the Treasure Coast, Fairwinds is known for
   its excellent condition and spectacular greens.

       Owned and operated by St. Lucie County, Fairwinds is a public
   course with a private flair.


